nager（移除全局双写）\n```\n\n---\n\n### 建议方案\n\n保持握手/lock 在用户级不动，**只把 Work Item 的状态文件迁到项目级**。改动面：\n\n| 文件 | 改动 |\n|------|------|\n| `Daemon.ts` | StateManager 不再 isDaemonGlobal；EventLogger basePath 改用项目路径 |\n| `sf-state-transition.ts` | 移除全局层写入，只保留项目层 |\n| `sf-state-read.ts` | 移除对全局层的回退 |\n| `RecoverySystem.ts` | 路径从 daemon-global 改为 project-scoped |\n\n要我用 Change Request 工作流来执行这个重构吗？","time":{"start":1780210182826,"end":1780210196928},"id":"prt_e7ccbaaaa001Wk1o9madgBH71D","sessionID":"ses_183dd3320ffeEB0AiZQ55MG54v","messageID":"msg_e7ccb80e3001YFuVzOSmbcWTIJ"},{"reason":"stop","snapshot":"69e2fba2705b7a28a908b5b97cb2cf54c7dcf26f","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":141618,"input":8503,"output":693,"reasoning":454,"cache":{"write":0,"read":131968}},"cost":0.005175079,"id":"prt_e7ccbe3110013cVAJDDFprTwQQ","sessionID":"ses_183dd3320ffeEB0AiZQ55MG54v","messageID":"msg_e7ccb80e3001YFuVzOSmbcWTIJ"}]},{"info":{"role":"user","time":{"created":1780210378261},"agent":"sf-orchestrator","model":{"providerID":"deepseek","modelID":"deepseek-v4-pro"},"summary":{"diffs":[{"file":".kiro/specs/v6-architecture-overview/artifacts/correctness-property-allocation.json","patch":"Index: .kiro/specs/v6-architecture-overview/artifacts/correctness-property-allocation.json\n===================================================================\n--- .kiro/specs/v6-architecture-overview/artifacts/correctness-property-allocation.json\t\n+++ .kiro/specs/v6-architecture-overview/artifacts/correctness-property-allocation.json\t\n@@ -1,185 +1,1 @@\n-{\r\n-  \"schema_version\": \"1.0\",\r\n-  \"properties\": [\r\n-    {\r\n-      \"id\": \"1\",\r\n-      \"title\": \"Single Source of Truth\",\r\n-      \"validates\": [\"30.1\", \"1.1\", \"4.1\"],\r\n-      \"owners\": [\"daemon-core\"]\r\n-    },\r\n-    {\r\n-      \"id\": \"2\",\r\n-      \"title\": \"Event Bus Traversal\",\r\n-      \"validates\": [\"30.2\"],\r\n-      \"owners\": [\"daemon-core\", \"observability\"]\r\n-    },\r\n-    {\r\n-      \"id