 门槛 2：北极星（10 类场景 5 分钟内定位根因） | SLO / 演练 | 每类场景的根因定位演练脚本平均 < 5 分钟；10 类全部通过 |\r\n+| 门槛 3：崩溃恢复（10 次随机 kill） | fault-injection | 随机在 workflow 不同阶段 kill Daemon，恢复后数据完整性 100% |\r\n+| 门槛 4：OpenClaw 端到端 | integration | 通过 OpenClaw 驱动 CLI 完成一次完整 spec 创建 + 执行 |\r\n+| 门槛 5：性能 | perf | Daemon 启动 < 3 s；事件写入 < 5 ms/event；standard 模式事件日志 < 1 GB/天 |\r\n+| 门槛 6：文档完整 | doc lint | 架构文档 + 用户手册齐全；Correctness Properties 15+ 条全部有下游归属 |\r\n+\r\n+**决议**：任一门槛未过 → 不打 V6.0 stable tag（REQ-27.2）。\r\n+\r\n+### 4. 不使用 PBT 的场景\r\n+\r\n+下述内容**不**用 PBT：\r\n+- OpenCode 外部行为（由 Adapter 隔离，直接集成测试即可）；\r\n+- LLM Provider 响应（外部服务，不是我们的代码）；\r\n+- 真实 Telegram 消息投递（OpenClaw 职责）；\r\n+- 平台安装流程、权限目录创建等一次性操作（SMOKE 即可）；\r\n+- 发版清单 / 里程碑产出 / 治理流程（SMOKE + 审查）。\r\n+\r\n","additions":1242,"deletions":0,"status":"added"}]},"id":"msg_e7ccea5f1001g53oIlRqxpEf7h","sessionID":"ses_183dd3320ffeEB0AiZQ55MG54v"},"parts":[{"type":"text","text":"同意","id":"prt_e7ccea5f2001NjQXyJ6X5PXcde","sessionID":"ses_183dd3320ffeEB0AiZQ55MG54v","messageID":"msg_e7ccea5f1001g53oIlRqxpEf7h"}]},{"info":{"parentID":"msg_e7ccea5f1001g53oIlRqxpEf7h","role":"assistant","mode":"sf-orchestrator","agent":"sf-orchestrator","path":{"cwd":"D:\\code\\temp\\SpecForge","root":"D:\\code\\temp\\SpecForge"},"cost":0.000823339,"tokens":{"total":141952,"input":55,"output":62,"reasoning":267,"cache":{"write":0,"read":141568}},"modelID":"deepseek-v4-pro","providerID":"deepseek","time":{"created":1780210378282,"completed":1780210386988},"finish":"tool-calls","id":"msg_e7ccea62a001bNONTKFHTaMR2z","sessionID":"ses_183dd3320ffeEB0AiZQ55MG54v"},"parts":[{"snapshot":"69e2fba2705b7a28a908b5b97cb2cf54c7dcf26f","type":"step-start","id":"prt_e7cceab38001NL7FGm9CBYpFeQ","sessionID":"ses_183dd3320ffeEB0AiZQ55MG54v","messageID":"msg_e7ccea62a001bNONTKFHTaMR2z"},{"type":"reasoning","text":"The user agrees to the refactoring plan. I should start a Change Request workflow. Let me load the skill and create a new Work Item.\n\nActually, looking at the workflow types:\n- change_reques